类 DefaultStoreFileManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.DefaultStoreFileManager
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    StoreFileManager

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
class DefaultStoreFileManager
extends Object
implements StoreFileManager
    Default implementation of StoreFileManager. Not thread-safe.

      • storefiles

        private volatile org.apache.hbase.thirdparty.com.google.common.collect.ImmutableList<HStoreFile> storefiles
        List of store files inside this store. This is an immutable list that is atomically replaced when its contents change.

      • compactedfiles

        private volatile org.apache.hbase.thirdparty.com.google.common.collect.ImmutableList<HStoreFile> compactedfiles
        List of compacted files inside this store that needs to be excluded in reads because further new reads will be using only the newly created files out of compaction. These compacted files will be deleted/cleared once all the existing readers on these compacted files are done.

      • getCandidateFilesForRowKeyBefore

        public final Iterator<HStoreFile> getCandidateFilesForRowKeyBefore(KeyValue targetKey)
        从接口复制的说明: StoreFileManager
        Gets initial, full list of candidate store files to check for row-key-before.
        指定者:
        getCandidateFilesForRowKeyBefore 在接口中 StoreFileManager
        参数:
        targetKey - The key that is the basis of the search.
        返回:
        The files that may have the key less than or equal to targetKey, in reverse order of new-ness, and preference for target key.

      • updateCandidateFilesForRowKeyBefore

        public Iterator<HStoreFile> updateCandidateFilesForRowKeyBefore(Iterator<HStoreFile> candidateFiles,
                                                                KeyValue targetKey,
                                                                Cell candidate)
        从接口复制的说明: StoreFileManager
        Updates the candidate list for finding row key before. Based on the list of candidates remaining to check from getCandidateFilesForRowKeyBefore, targetKey and current candidate, may trim and reorder the list to remove the files where a better candidate cannot be found.
        指定者:
        updateCandidateFilesForRowKeyBefore 在接口中 StoreFileManager
        参数:
        candidateFiles - The candidate files not yet checked for better candidates - return value from StoreFileManager.getCandidateFilesForRowKeyBefore(KeyValue), with some files already removed.
        targetKey - The key to search for.
        candidate - The current best candidate found.
        返回:
        The list to replace candidateFiles.
